name: POSEIDON
description:
Crypto Chaos, A collection created by Alex Gray & Calvyn Justus & Alex Gray.

After thousands of years, statues from ancient Greece have been recovered, they have been digitally downloaded and activated into the meta-verse. The gods are returning, virtually.

One Edition of each god, starting with:

#1 POSEIDON: One of the twelve Olympians, the violent and ill-tempered god of the sea.

Sound on for the full Experience. 4k quality.
